      Who owns Tops Diner?
      Tops, which opened in 1942, has been approved for expansion by the Hudson County Planning Board. Owners Jimmy and John Golemis, whose father George bought the diner in 1972, could not be reached for comment on the expansion.Jul 17, 2019

      What Is Tops Diner?
      Tops Diner is America's premier family-owned diner, serving over 15,000 hungry customers exactly what they want each week. Established in 1942, Tops remains a staple and institution for Newark as well as a destination.

      What are they building next to Tops Diner?
      Next, an all-new diner structure will be built on the adjacent, existing parking area. Finally, the current Tops Diner building will be razed, creating additional parking spaces. The target date to complete the work and unveil the new Tops is March 2021.Nov 7, 2019
